WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.900
A Normal Day.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.900
I teach English.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.900
Today, I left the house early

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.900
to go to the gym.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.900
After the gym, I went to the dentist

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:35.900
because my teeth were hurting.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.900
The doctor examined me and told me

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.900
that I could eat in two hours,

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.900
"Enjoy your meal."

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.900
After I left the dentist,

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:01.900
I walked up an uphill street.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:07.900
Walking there was a bit difficult.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.900
After that, I entered a downhill street

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:19.900
and walking there was easier.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.900
On the way, I saw my friend.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:29.900
I always see him there.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:31.900
He was standing looking upset

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:35.900
because a thief

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:42.900
robbed the shop near him.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:46.900
My friend is an honest man

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:53.900
and he hates anyone who steals.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.900
He always says,

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:02.900
"A thief never feels satisfied."

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.900
Because I was in a hurry,

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:08.900
I told him,

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:12.900
"Don't be upset with me.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:14.900
I am in a hurry

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:18.900
and I will see you later."

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:23.900
After all this running around,

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:28.000
I went to work a bit late.